29:14.753 --> 29:16.667
MONICA:
I'm not comfortable here.

29:16.711 --> 29:18.060
Yeah, it's pretty stinky.

29:18.104 --> 29:19.235
And sticky.Yeah, which means

29:19.279 --> 29:20.628
Liam will not
be here, okay?

