where the locals go.

29:22.804 --> 29:24.806
Local murderers?

29:24.850 --> 29:25.938
CRISTAL:
You did

29:25.981 --> 29:27.766
the right thing, Fallon.Well, clearly,

29:27.809 --> 29:29.768
I don't have much
practice with that,

29:29.811 --> 29:31.247
