29:33.249 --> 29:36.165
Which means that Serena van der
Woodsen knockoff gets him.

29:36.209 --> 29:39.690
That's fine. So I am sorry
for bringing you all here.

29:39.734 --> 29:41.997
I wish we could leave
this mountain ASAP,

29:42.041 --> 29:44.043
but unfortunately, Blake
has the jet in Belgium,

29:44.086 --> 29:46.349
and it won't be able
to get us till morning.We can fly commercial.

29:46.393 --> 29:49.004
Mm. Yeah, we could also eat
that mystery meat chili,

29:49.048 --> 29:50.832
but we're not gonna
do that either.

29:50.876 --> 29:52.791
Look, we're
stuck here,

29:52.834 --> 29:54.836
so let's just salvage
what's left of this girls trip

29:54.880 --> 29:56.795
and have a girls
night, okay?

29:56.838 --> 29:58.144
Drinks are on me.

29:58.187 --> 30:00.581
'Cause I am a miserable loser.

30:05.194 --> 30:08.154
Hey. We could really use
this table for people.

30:08.197 --> 30:09.938
Okay if I check your stuff?

30:09.982 --> 30:11.418
Yeah, that's fine.Thanks.

30:12.419 --> 30:14.551
Hey, hey, hey, hey, hey.

30:14.595 --> 30:16.075
Easy with the leather
on that bag.

30:16.118 --> 30:17.250
Okay.

30:17.293 --> 30:18.294
Well...

30:18.338 --> 30:19.774
you were right.

30:19.818 --> 30:21.776
Chasing Liam here
was a terrible idea.

30:21.820 --> 30:23.734
I'm so sorry
it didn't work out.

30:23.778 --> 30:27.260
I know we're not
super close, Fallon,

30:27.303 --> 30:30.524
but if I can help you
in any way,

30:30.567 --> 30:32.308
just let me know.

30:32.352 --> 30:35.442
I mean, touching your hair would
make me feel a little better.

30:35.485 --> 30:37.313
Not here.

30:37.357 --> 30:40.360
Okay. So, later, then?

30:40.403 --> 30:42.057
I'm a miserable loser, too.

30:42.101 --> 30:44.190
And I thought that getting
away would help me forget

30:44.233 --> 30:47.323
that I kissed a man
that's not Steven, but, uh...

30:47.367 --> 30:49.804
