32:11.799 --> 32:14.410
So why don't you come up
with another plan...

32:14.454 --> 32:17.022
and maybe I'll entertain it.

32:17.065 --> 32:18.675
Hmm.

32:18.719 --> 32:20.503
Troops,

32:20.547 --> 32:23.985
