and our cell phones?

32:58.150 --> 33:00.630
Whose idea was it to
come to a shady bar

33:00.674 --> 33:04.199
on the side of a
mountain in Idaho?

33:04.243 --> 33:06.462
Well, it's not my fault.

33:06.506 --> 33:07.550
It may be my fault.

33:07.594 --> 33:08.551
Look,

33:08.595 --> 33:09.552
