33:09.596 --> 33:11.163
Somebody needs to pay.

33:11.206 --> 33:12.381
Oh! I have my phone.

33:12.425 --> 33:14.514
I'll just call Jeff.
He'll send us money.

33:14.557 --> 33:16.385
And it's dead.

33:16.429 --> 33:18.387
You want to buy
a used phone?

33:20.215 --> 33:22.348
I'm gonna win that money
for you, Fallon.

33:25.177 --> 33:27.309
♪ You keep saying

33:27.353 --> 33:28.832
♪ You got something for me

33:28.876 --> 33:30.182
SAM: Well, it is
enough money to pay

33:30.225 --> 33:31.531
our tab and get us out
of this dump.

33:31.574 --> 33:33.533
Yeah, but that's
only if you win.

33:33.576 --> 33:35.796
Girl's got moves
she didn't learn at cotillion.

33:35.839 --> 33:38.538
♪ You've been a-messin'

33:38.581 --> 33:39.713
You're ruining that song
for me!

33:39.756 --> 33:41.454
God,

33:41.497 --> 33:43.064
I have to go up
there, don't I?

33:43.108 --> 33:45.414
It's unbearable.
Kirby.

33:45.458 --> 33:47.721
