and made a huge mistake

36:01.289 --> 36:03.204
by sleeping with my ex-husband.

36:03.248 --> 36:04.336
Your ex-husband?

36:04.379 --> 36:06.207
Mark Jennings.

36:06.251 --> 36:08.340
Life can take you in directions
you can't control.

36:08.383 --> 36:12.213
Never in my wildest
dreams did I imagine

36:12.257 --> 36:13.780
I was gonna end up
back in Atlanta,

36:13.823 --> 36:15.347
