36:22.441 --> 36:24.573
What should
I do, Fallon?

36:24.617 --> 36:27.489
I'm afraid he'll go crazy
if this baby isn't his.

36:27.533 --> 36:30.318
Well, you're not wrong.

36:30.362 --> 36:32.320
I say move to Idaho.

36:32.364 --> 36:33.974
