and that baby.

36:56.953 --> 36:59.173
No matter whose it is.

37:09.575 --> 37:11.577
Ashley isn't pressing charges.

37:11.620 --> 37:12.708
Her friends
saw you come in here,

37:12.752 --> 37:13.927
so she paid someone
to steal your stuff,

37:13.970 --> 37:15.320
in retaliation for what

37:15.363 --> 37:16.408
