over here did to her.

37:16.451 --> 37:18.323
Hey, Liam.

37:18.366 --> 37:19.585
I'm sorry, okay?

37:19.628 --> 37:21.151
I think there's been
a huge misunderstanding.

37:21.195 --> 37:22.414
No, I think
I understand perfectly, Fallon.

37:22.457 --> 37:24.416
You came here
to destroy my relationship.

37:24.459 --> 37:25.852
That's not true.

37:25.895 --> 37:27.332
Okay.And, for the record,
your girlfriend

37:27.375 --> 37:28.507
