I couldn't live without you.

38:04.630 --> 38:07.459
Now I can't
stand the sight of you.

38:17.599 --> 38:19.819
How was the
girls trip?

38:20.863 --> 38:22.387
Youwere invited?

38:22.430 --> 38:25.433
Mm. You missed quite
an adventure, Alexis.

38:27.043 --> 38:28.958
I knew youwere gone,

38:29.002 --> 38:31.961
after what seemed
like a 15-hour float.

38:32.005 --> 38:33.485
I'm sorry I bailed
on you, but I didn't

38:33.528 --> 38:35.313
want to make you sadder.

38:35.356 --> 38:37.532
This type of sadder.

38:37.576 --> 38:38.881
Thank you, Sam.

38:40.318 --> 38:41.493
Well, while I was floating,

38:41.536 --> 38:43.669
I realized
that I don't have SAD.

38:43.712 --> 38:45.323
I am sad.

38:45.366 --> 38:47.455
Nobody wants me here, and

38:47.499 --> 38:49.022
nobody needs me.
And Cristal

38:49.065 --> 38:50.850
has weaseled her way
into this family,

38:50.893 --> 38:52.852
and now she's been crowned

38:52.895 --> 38:56.290
as the new queen of the manor.

38:56.334 --> 38:58.466
Meanwhile,
what am I doing?

38:58.510 --> 39:00.294
I just feel...

39:00.338 --> 39:01.643
directionless.

39:01.687 --> 39:03.079
I get that.

39:03.123 --> 39:05.647
While I was escaping,

39:05.691 --> 39:08.476
I realized that
I've done things I regret.

39:08.520 --> 39:10.870
Steven has done things I regret.

39:10.913 --> 39:13.220
But it's not healthy
to dwell on them.

39:13.263 --> 39:15.570
So I'm moving forward,

39:15.614 --> 39:17.224
taking care of myself.

39:17.267 --> 39:18.486
I'm sorry you're sad.

39:18.530 --> 39:21.663
Don't worry.
I will be just fine.

39:24.666 --> 39:28.278
I'm not sure I can say the same
for the weasel queen.

39:30.411 --> 39:32.370
Where's Mom?

39:33.414 --> 39:35.634
Mom didn't get on the plane.

39:36.678 --> 39:38.158
No message.

39:38.201 --> 39:40.203
No phone call.

39:41.204 --> 39:43.424
I know you warned me,

39:43.468 --> 39:46.209
but that's just brutal.

39:46.253 --> 39:47.776
I don't know what to say.

39:47.820 --> 39:49.561
You were right, Mon.

39:49.604 --> 39:52.128
This family's been broken
for years,

39:52.172 --> 39:53.608
and I thought
one dream

39:53.652 --> 39:56.829
and one phone call
would bring us together.

39:56.872 --> 39:58.570
It's not you.

39:58.613 --> 39:59.832
It's her.

39:59.875 --> 40:02.617
We need to just forget
about our mother.

40:02.661 --> 40:04.706
All she does is
make us miserable.

40:06.534 --> 40:08.275
Well...

40:08.318 --> 40:10.930
thanks for not saying
"I told you so."

40:12.453 --> 40:15.021
Wish Mom could see what a good
person you turned out to be.

40:20.896 --> 40:24.030
♪ Worry, worry...

40:24.073 --> 40:25.553
What do you want, Kirby?

40:27.512 --> 40:30.428
I'm sorry for the way things
turned out with you and Liam.

40:30.471 --> 40:31.994
Just don't.

40:32.038 --> 40:33.474
Sorry.

40:33.518 --> 40:34.780
Stop saying you're sorry.

40:34.823 --> 40:35.998
Sorry.

40:38.436 --> 40:40.786
I just wanted to say
that I'm here for you

40:40.829 --> 40:42.788
if you need a friend.

40:42.831 --> 40:44.572
Anything.

40:44.616 --> 40:46.095
I'm here.

40:46.139 --> 40:49.272
Just please
leave me alone, Kirby. Okay?

40:49.316 --> 40:51.536
♪ But if I falter

40:51.579 --> 40:54.495
♪ Well, at least
it was my mistake ♪

40:54.539 --> 40:56.584
You know, it was like
you see in the movies.

40:56.628 --> 40:59.544
We just sat around
and gossiped over

40:59.587 --> 41:01.546
cheese plates
and sauvignon blanc.

41:01.589 --> 41:04.723
Frankly, I thought those girls
were gonna drive you crazy.

41:04.766 --> 41:06.507
But while you were
gone, I realized

41:06.551 --> 41:08.553
that I was the one
driving you crazy

41:08.596 --> 41:11.643
with my overzealousness
about doctors.

41:11.686 --> 41:13.514
So...

41:13.558 --> 41:15.168
♪ Well, nothing
really changes at all ♪

41:16.648 --> 41:18.650
♪ Am I jaded...

41:18.693 --> 41:20.782
Blake, I need
to tell you something.I know.

41:20.826 --> 41:22.567
